                            </h3>
            <h1 itemprop="headline" class="story-heading">Investigating Familyœôòùs Wealth, Chinaœôòùs Leader Signals a Change</h1>

                        <div class="story-meta-footer">
                                

<p class="byline-dateline"><span class="byline" itemprop="author creator" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person" >By <span class="byline-author" data-byline-name="MICHAEL FORSYTHE" itemprop="name">MICHAEL FORSYTHE</span>, </span><span class="byline" itemprop="author creator" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person" ><span class="byline-author" data-byline-name="CHRIS BUCKLEY" itemprop="name">CHRIS BUCKLEY</span> and </span><span class="byline" itemprop="author creator" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person" ><span class="byline-author" data-byline-name="JONATHAN ANSFIELD" itemprop="name">JONATHAN ANSFIELD</span></span><time class="dateline" datetime="2014-04-19">APRIL 19, 2014</time>
</p>                <div class="inside-story">
                    <span class="menu-label">Inside</span>
                    <ul class="inside-story-menu"></ul>
                </div>
            </div><!-- close story-meta-footer -->
        </div><!-- close story-meta -->
    </header>

    
